<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 12:11:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>警告赎罪日战争迫在眉睫的摩萨德前负责人去世，享年 98 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/former-mossad-head-who-warned-of-imminent-yom-kippur-war-dies-at-98/0000018c-c98b-ddba-abad-cbab791f0000</link><description>兹维·扎米尔警告说，如果“以色列政策没有发生深远的变化，战争就在预料之中” ■ 这位前摩萨德主席留下了卓越的服务遗产，摩萨德和以色列总统热烈纪念</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 11:39:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/former-mossad-head-who-warned-of-imminent-yom-kippur-war-dies-at-98/0000018c-c98b-ddba-abad-cbab791f0000</guid></item><item><title>丹尼斯·罗斯：在加沙，“内塔尼亚胡的极右翼部长并没有生活在现实中”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-02/ty-article-podcast/dennis-ross-on-gaza-netanyahus-far-right-ministers-arent-living-in-reality/0000018c-c6bc-ddba-abad-c6bd77b30000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 11:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-02/ty-article-podcast/dennis-ross-on-gaza-netanyahus-far-right-ministers-arent-living-in-reality/0000018c-c6bc-ddba-abad-c6bd77b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长称本-格维尔“越界”并干扰警方批准抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-says-ben-gvir-crossed-the-line-to-interfere-with-police-approvals-of-protests/0000018c-c94a-d4e1-ad8f-fdfbb6a20000</link><description>总检察长警告说，以色列国家安全部长告诉警方禁止左翼哈达什党举行抗议活动，这已经越界了。本-格维尔的办公室表示，总检察长“有一个非常明确的议程”，并且讨厌他</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 10:26:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-says-ben-gvir-crossed-the-line-to-interfere-with-police-approvals-of-protests/0000018c-c94a-d4e1-ad8f-fdfbb6a20000</guid></item><item><title>画面中缺失：哈马斯袭击前后的以色列家庭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/missing-from-the-frame-israeli-families-before-and-after-hamas-attack/0000018c-c579-d6c4-ab8d-e5fd1f6a0000</link><description>有你和没有你：一个特别的摄影项目展示了 10 月 7 日家庭成员被哈马斯抓走之前和之后拍摄的照片</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 10:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/missing-from-the-frame-israeli-families-before-and-after-hamas-attack/0000018c-c579-d6c4-ab8d-e5fd1f6a0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦和阿拉伯囚犯报告称，自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列监狱看守的暴力行为激增</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-arab-prisoners-report-surge-in-violence-by-israeli-guards-since-oct-7/0000018c-c6a2-ddba-abad-c6a3a6920000</link><description>以色列北部一所监狱的安全拘留者报告称，他们遭到狱警的殴打，并威胁称，如果他们拒绝亲吻以色列国旗，就会遭受暴力袭击。 ■ 司法部警告监狱部门，必须依法对待囚犯</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 07:41:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-arab-prisoners-report-surge-in-violence-by-israeli-guards-since-oct-7/0000018c-c6a2-ddba-abad-c6a3a6920000</guid></item><item><title>美国在该地区海军存在的减少对以色列来说不是好兆头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/reduced-u-s-naval-presence-in-the-region-does-not-bode-well-for-israel/0000018c-c6e1-ddba-abad-c6e189a60000</link><description>真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉可能将美国的重新部署解读为承担更多风险的机会 ■ 本杰明·内塔尼亚胡和美国总统乔·拜登最近进行了一系列紧张的对话，主要集中在以色列领导人对巴勒斯坦权力机构的不屑一顾的态度</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 04:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/reduced-u-s-naval-presence-in-the-region-does-not-bode-well-for-israel/0000018c-c6e1-ddba-abad-c6e189a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院判定内塔尼亚胡及其盗贼团伙惨败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-deals-netanyahu-and-his-band-of-thieves-a-decisive-defeat/0000018c-c74d-ddba-abad-c7ede2eb0000</link><description>周日最高法院以一票之差恢复了对以色列国的形容词“民主”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 04:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-deals-netanyahu-and-his-band-of-thieves-a-decisive-defeat/0000018c-c74d-ddba-abad-c7ede2eb0000</guid></item><item><title>阵亡以色列士兵的父母致美国布林肯：停止战争是“历史性错误”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-in-gaza-far-right-ministers-call-for-control-of-gaza-settlements/0000018c-c81b-ddba-abad-cabbb6f60000</link><description>以色列空军袭击叙利亚，摧毁黎巴嫩南部真主党目标 ■ 以色列国防军在加沙近东救济工程处一所学校附近找到哈马斯火箭发射器 ■ 报告：33 人因涉嫌与摩萨德合作而在土耳其被捕 ■ 阵亡以色列国防军士兵的父母向布林肯表示：“阻止战争将是历史性的错误。 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵丧生；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 21,978 人死亡，57,697 人受伤</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 03:04:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-02/ty-article-live/idf-soldier-killed-in-gaza-far-right-ministers-call-for-control-of-gaza-settlements/0000018c-c81b-ddba-abad-cabbb6f60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院驳斥内塔尼亚胡的独裁谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-01/ty-article/.highlight/israels-supreme-court-strikes-down-netanyahus-autocratic-lies/0000018c-c643-d6c4-ab8d-e7f74d2a0000</link><description>这是以色列历史上最重要的案件之一：法院的裁决推翻了内塔尼亚胡政府对以色列社会极不受欢迎的神权吞并主义接管，以及随之而来的令人震惊的荒谬谎言</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:54:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-01/ty-article/.highlight/israels-supreme-court-strikes-down-netanyahus-autocratic-lies/0000018c-c643-d6c4-ab8d-e7f74d2a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列央行四年来首次降息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-cuts-interest-rate-for-first-time-in-two-years/0000018c-c6bc-d6c4-ab8d-e7bc10390000</link><description>由于通胀缓和以及加沙战争对经济前景的担忧，失业率下降了四分之一个百分点至 4.5%。央行现在担心的是政府支出急剧增加，因为它修改了2024年预算以满足战争需要</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:54:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-cuts-interest-rate-for-first-time-in-two-years/0000018c-c6bc-d6c4-ab8d-e7bc10390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学停课八名声称在社交媒体帖子上支持哈马斯的学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-suspends-eight-students-claiming-they-supported-hamas-on-social-media/0000018c-c69a-ddba-abad-c6bb88f60000</link><description>海法大学采取这一行动之前，校长声称学生的继续存在可能会引发“极端情况”。自 10 月 7 日以来，超过 100 名以色列学生（几乎全是阿拉伯人）因涉嫌表达支持哈马斯而面临纪律处分</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:39:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-university-suspends-eight-students-claiming-they-supported-hamas-on-social-media/0000018c-c69a-ddba-abad-c6bb88f60000</guid></item><item><title>这位拯救以色列脆弱民主的女人——暂时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/the-woman-who-saved-israels-fragile-democracy-for-now/0000018c-c69a-d6c4-ab8d-e7beabb30000</link><description>前最高法院院长埃丝特·哈尤特周一主持了一项裁决，有效地终止了政府的司法改革，为以色列社会带来了巨大的帮助。但以色列仍然像以前一样分裂，并且在战争结束后仍然如此</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 20:22:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/the-woman-who-saved-israels-fragile-democracy-for-now/0000018c-c69a-d6c4-ab8d-e7beabb30000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长们猛烈抨击最高法院“危险、非法”的裁决；拉皮德：“司法保护”以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ministers-slam-court-dangerous-ruling-lapid-justices-safeguarded-israelis/0000018c-c640-d4e1-ad8f-fef1fd780000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的政府部长们抨击了法院裁决的时机和内容，指责其破坏了加沙的“团结”和以色列国防军士兵。 反对派政界人士赞扬了这一裁决，称围绕司法政变的危机导致了10月7日</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 19:17:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ministers-slam-court-dangerous-ruling-lapid-justices-safeguarded-israelis/0000018c-c640-d4e1-ad8f-fef1fd780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预备役军人周一在加沙地带北部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/israeli-army-reservist-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip-fighting-on-monday/0000018c-c639-d4e1-ad8f-feb9f1760000</link><description>24 岁的 Amichai Yisrael Yehoshua Oster 被爆炸装置炸死。在同一场战斗中，另有11名士兵受伤，其中两人伤势严重</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 18:42:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/israeli-army-reservist-killed-in-northern-gaza-strip-fighting-on-monday/0000018c-c639-d4e1-ad8f-feb9f1760000</guid></item><item><title>其基布兹宣布，56 岁以色列人自 10 月 7 日起失踪，被宣告死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/56-year-old-israeli-thought-missing-since-october-7-declared-dead-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-c5be-d6c4-ab8d-e5bec2a10000</link><description>伊兰·韦斯 (Ilan Weiss) 的妻子和女儿希里·韦斯 (Shiri Weiss) 和诺加·韦斯 (Noga Weiss) 从贝埃里 (Be&amp;#39;eri) 被绑架到加沙，并于 11 月 26 日作为与哈马斯人质交易的一部分获释</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 16:22:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/56-year-old-israeli-thought-missing-since-october-7-declared-dead-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-c5be-d6c4-ab8d-e5bec2a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院驳回内塔尼亚胡政府司法政变法限制其权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-set-to-release-ruling-on-netanyahu-govt-key-judicial-coup-law/0000018c-c01f-d3e0-abac-d8bf3c2d0000</link><description>以色列议会7月通过的旨在取消法院推翻被认为不合理的政府决定的权力的修正案在15名法官中的8名法官的裁决中无效 ■ 15名法官中的12名裁定最高法院有权行使权力基本法的司法审查</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 16:16:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-set-to-release-ruling-on-netanyahu-govt-key-judicial-coup-law/0000018c-c01f-d3e0-abac-d8bf3c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，一名坦桑尼亚父亲前往以色列寻找儿子被杀的答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-tanzanian-father-journeys-to-israel-to-seek-answers-for-his-sons-killing-on-oct-7/0000018c-c516-d4e1-ad8f-fdb7243a0000</link><description>坦桑尼亚学生约书亚·莫勒尔在抵达以色列基布兹学习农业几周后，在哈马斯的袭击中被谋杀。两个月来，他的父亲一直希望儿子能回到他身边——直到一段记录他被谋杀的视频开始在社交媒体上流传</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 15:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-tanzanian-father-journeys-to-israel-to-seek-answers-for-his-sons-killing-on-oct-7/0000018c-c516-d4e1-ad8f-fdb7243a0000</guid></item><item><title>由于对加沙战争的预算担忧，以色列政府质疑情报部的必要性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/amid-budget-concerns-over-war-israeli-govt-question-need-for-intelligence-ministry/0000018c-c56c-d4e1-ad8f-fdfd253f0000</link><description>虽然该部的任务是协调以色列各个情报机构之间的关系，但这些机构并不在该部之下运作。这是财政部因效率问题建议关闭的十个办事处之一</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 15:27:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/amid-budget-concerns-over-war-israeli-govt-question-need-for-intelligence-ministry/0000018c-c56c-d4e1-ad8f-fdfd253f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长敦促任命内塔尼亚胡的私人医生和心腹为名誉领事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-pushed-to-appoint-netanyahus-personal-physician-an-honorary-consul/0000018c-c467-d6c4-ab8d-e5f7ff3a0000</link><description>外交部长伊莱·科恩“向我保证这将会发生”，兹维·伯科维茨博士说，他的任命是在部长的一次不同寻常的干预后获得批准的。他被认为是内塔尼亚胡夫妇最亲密的知己</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 14:57:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-pushed-to-appoint-netanyahus-personal-physician-an-honorary-consul/0000018c-c467-d6c4-ab8d-e5f7ff3a0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦活动家将在未经审判的情况下被关押四个月——他在脸书上发帖称不是他的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-activist-held-without-trial-for-4-months-for-facebook-posts-he-says-arent-his/0000018c-c4c7-ddba-abad-c6e70cbd0000</link><description>律师告诉《国土报》，自战争开始以来，许多巴勒斯坦人未经审判就被关押，因为这些指控通常不会导致达成这一协议；以色列国防军表示正在“调查”家人在逮捕期间遭受暴力的指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 12:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-activist-held-without-trial-for-4-months-for-facebook-posts-he-says-arent-his/0000018c-c4c7-ddba-abad-c6e70cbd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>